title: Super Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Chinese, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Popular, well-established, predominantly Indian (along with Chinese) restaurant, with extensive vegetarian menu of 30+ items. Some vegan items available on vegetarian menu. Vegans please inquire about use of cheese (paneer) or cream in sauces and gravies.
